oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Advertising; Exhibitions; Flags; Woodcuts (prints);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (blue and red on white) announcing US ... Eh?: New Work by Alex MacAskill and Cory Wasnewsky closing reception as the Sawtooth Print Shop leaves the East Side Art Stumble in Nashville on July 9. Poster features a woodcut of an American flag with the Canadian maple leaf in place of the fifty stars.
